Method Detail

confirm

void confirm(Message msg)
Confirms the message to the external system. If the Message.getState() is MsgStateEnum.OK, then confirms the message as OK, if it's MsgStateEnum.FAILED, then confirms the message as Failed.

Parameters:
msg - the message to confirm

getExternalSystems

Set<ExternalSystemExtEnum> getExternalSystems()
Returns supported external systems.

the supported external systems
